---
title: Sirloin Steak and Handcut Rosemary Chips with Garlic & Rosemary Butter and Garlicky Green Beans
description: This Sirloin Steak and Handcut Rosemary Chips is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sirloin-steak-and-handcut-rosemary-chips-523c4c0c-a70e93d1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sirloin-steak-and-handcut-rosemary-chips-616e7db680a2e9172024598d-2e6fd096.pdf
